%section.introduction

  %h2 Welcome, neighbor! 
  %p
    In order make the most out of Vicini, we need to know a little about you and
    where you live. This information is used only to provide your location. 

  %p Privacy is important to us. Below is our ethos:

  %ul
    %li Your data is used for only its intended use.
    %li Your data is never bartered or sold.
    %li Your data is never given to advertisers.
    %li Your data may be kept indefinitely.
    %li Data is given to law enforcement only when the legal process is followed.
 
= simple_form_for @user do |f|
  - if @user.errors.any?
    #error_explanation
      %h2= "#{pluralize(@user.errors.count, "error")} prohibited this user from being saved:"
      %ul
        - @user.errors.full_messages.each do |msg|
          %li= msg
  .actions
    = f.input :first_name, placeholder: 'First Name'
    = f.input :last_name, placeholder: 'Last Name'
    = f.input :address1, placeholder: 'Street Address'
    = f.input :address2
    = f.input :city, placeholder: 'City'
    = f.input :state, placeholder: 'State'
    = f.input :zip, placeholder: 'Zip'
    = f.submit t('users.new') 
